         <abstract id="aspace_61cfc18d3fcdac9e1da75fdaf76c390b">Correspondence, lectures, and printed material compiled by John Gamble Kirkwood during his tenure at Yale University. The lectures are on statistical mechanics and thermodynamics. Half of the papers are made up of offprints of articles in chemistry by others.</abstract>
